The paper discusses the use of social media platforms for spreading extremist ideologies and predicting civil unrest events. This falls under the categories of social media intelligence (cs.SI), cybersecurity (cs.CR), cyber-physical systems (cs.CY), natural language processing (cs.CL), and social network analysis (cs.SD). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
